cali.Rd

Calibrate algorithms

Usage

cali_DDS(fitness, x_Min, x_Max, x_Init = NA, max_iter = 100, r = 0.2, ...)

cali_UVS(
  fitness,
  x_Min,
  x_Max,
  x_Init = NA,
  max_n_loop = 10,
  n_1_search = 8,
  ...
)

Arguments

fitness

fitness function

x_Min, x_Max, x_Init

minimal, maximal initial parameter

max_iter

maximal number of iteration

r

parameter for algorithm

...

other parameters

max_n_loop

maximal number of loops

n_1_search

maximal number in one loop

DDS

dynamically dimensioned search (DDS) calibration algorithm

UVS

Univariable search algorithmus
